We have few task that should be resolved in this project:

1. Generate secret
Secret - is some phrase with one or more words that does not contains any duplicates.
Application should inform user if there are some duplicated words in phrase

2. Store secret
Each time when user starts application his secret should be shown.

3. Add functionality to validate answers.
Answer - is some phrase that contains one word from secret.
User will be informed if answer don't commit requirements, e.g. answer contains more then one secret word or there are not intersection with secret.
In this task we want to show number of used word is secret phrase.



First of all we'll create application for Russian users.
This application will work in windows OS using .NET 4.0+ environment
We don't use any network connection at first time but we plan to check secret popularity with Bing or Google service in future.
